&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the VP of Platform &amp;amp; Solutions Marketing, the Director of Product Marketing for Platform &amp;amp; Drupal owns solution GTM for Acquia&#39;s platform and Drupal offering end to end. This is the technical-buyer practice: PaaS plus Drupal, sold to CTOs, CIOs, and CISOs who care about control, performance, security, and total cost of ownership. You own positioning, messaging, sales plays, and launches, you manage a Product Marketing Manager, and you partner with our Drupal Technical Product Marketer. You must have real Drupal experience; this audience spots a non-practitioner immediately.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a leadership seat for someone who drives programs to completion. We use AI to do the job better, and everyone on this team demos and presents on stage. This role is a balance of strategy and fast paced execution where you will be expected to make decisions based on data and drive forward a plan based on data and evaluation of the market.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the solution GTM for our platform and Drupal offering end to end: the positioning, messaging, narrative, and sales plays. You set the strategy based on data and customer insight, not gut.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the content that carries the story to the Drupal community, technical buyers, and the field: the proof-driven narrative and the web, sales, and campaign assets behind it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own our competitive GTM for the solution: the positioning and plays that win competitive and displacement deals and drive cross-sell across the portfolio. (Competitive &amp;amp; Market Intelligence owns the intel; you own the go-to-market.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive product launches end to end. Own the launch calendar and the cross-functional program: lead the room, set the cadence, make the calls, and keep Product, Sales, Enablement, and Demand Gen aligned and shipping on time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build the technical-buyer narrative for CTO / CIO / CISO, and the TCO tools the field uses to win and defend deals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Sales Enablement on a value-selling spine (Signal &amp;gt; Value &amp;gt; Action): they author the artifacts, you set the language and prove adoption in real deals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and grow the Product Marketing Manager, and partner with the Drupal Evangelist to deliver one comprehensive GTM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
