&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Custom Proofs: &lt;/strong&gt;Design and execute impactful custom demonstrations and Proof-of-Concepts (PoCs) that clearly illustrate the business value of the Acquia platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competitive Positioning: &lt;/strong&gt;Position Acquia against key competitors through strong discovery and a clear point of view on fit, reinforcing Acquia’s unique value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
